com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.logging

Class WZAndroidLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.logging.WZLogger
      • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.logging.WZAndroidLogger

  • public class WZAndroidLogger
extends WZLogger
    The WZLogger implementation used by the Android version of the GoCoder SDK. This is the default logger registered when the SDK is initialized. It uses the standard Android Log API for output.
    See Also:
